column16: Carlos Gomez lines out sharply to second baseman Brandon Phillips.
Kyle Lohse out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Jay Bruce.   Jean Segura scores.

Jean Segura doubles (13) on a sharp line drive to left fielder Jason Bourgeois.   Gerardo Parra scores.    Rickie Weeks scores.  Jean Segura advances to 3rd, on a throwing error by left fielder Jason Bourgeois.
Khris Davis pops out to catcher Devin Mesoraco in foul territory.
Rickie Weeks walks.   Gerardo Parra to 2nd.
Yadier Molina singles on a ground ball to center fielder Billy Hamilton.
Randal Grichuk homers (3) on a fly ball to left center field.
Matt Szczur flies out to center fielder Billy Hamilton.
Logan Watkins flies out to center fielder Billy Hamilton.
Matt Adams flies out to left fielder Ryan Ludwick.
Matt Adams strikes out swinging.  Wild pitch by pitcher Ryan Dennick.   Matt Carpenter to 3rd.    Jon Jay to 2nd.    Matt Adams to 1st.
Wilmer Flores grounds into a double play, shortstop Zack Cozart to second baseman Brandon Phillips to first baseman Jack Hannahan.   Lucas Duda out at 2nd.
Dilson Herrera singles on a ground ball to shortstop Ramon Santiago.
Curtis Granderson homers (17) on a fly ball to right field.    David Wright scores.    Travis d'Arnaud scores.
Travis d'Arnaud singles on a line drive to center fielder Billy Hamilton.   David Wright to 2nd.
Lucas Duda pops out to third baseman Todd Frazier.
David Wright singles on a line drive to right fielder Jay Bruce.
Matt den Dekker bunt grounds out, pitcher Ryan Dennick to first baseman Brayan Pena.
Ryan Flaherty flies out to center fielder Billy Hamilton.
Jimmy Paredes grounds out sharply, third baseman Kristopher Negron to first baseman Todd Frazier.
